  "keyFeatures": [
    "Declarative Signatures — define tasks as typed input/output contracts instead of hand-crafted prompts",
    "Composable Modules — swap Predict, ChainOfThought, ReAct, and custom modules without rewriting logic",
    "Automatic Prompt Optimization — compile programs against a metric using MIPROv2, GEPA, and BootstrapFewShot",
    "Few-Shot Learning — automatically synthesize and select high-quality demonstrations",
    "Instruction Optimization — GEPA uses LM reflection to evolve and improve prompt instructions",
    "Fine-Tuning Integration — BetterTogether and BootstrapFinetune combine prompt and weight optimization",
    "Model Agnostic — works with OpenAI, Anthropic, local Ollama models, and any LiteLLM-compatible provider",
    "Evaluation Framework — built-in evaluation loop with customizable scoring metrics"
  ],
